# NETWORK::IS_ENTITY_IN_GHOST_COLLISION

## Summary
Returns true if this entity is intersecting other entities due to ghost mode (this may be the case after ghost mode is switched off)

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity

## Returns
* **BOOL**
